Project Hardening and Performance Optimizations

This plan tracks medium-priority cleanups, optimizations, and dead-code removal identified in the codebase review.

## Objectives
- Reduce redundant DB queries (e.g., Login calling `GetTOTPEnabled` twice).
- Prevent duplicate JWT parsing in `MFARequiredMiddleware`.
- Add missing database indexes (`auth_backup_codes.user_id` and `page_comment_likes`).
- Remove dead code across the auth package (unused `totp.go`, unused models, empty interfaces).
- Deduplicate repository methods (`SetTOTPSecret` vs `CreateTOTPSecret`).

## Scope
- `backend/internal/auth/handlers.go`
- `backend/internal/middleware/mfarequired.go`
- `backend/internal/migrations/` (new migration for indexes)
- `backend/internal/auth/totp.go` (delete)
- `backend/models/auth.go`
- `backend/internal/authhandler/handler.go`
- `backend/internal/auth/repository.go`
